name: Temoc
extBio: Hello! My name is Temoc. I am the official mascot of UT Dallas.Temoc is “comet” spelled backwards. My best friends are the UT Dallas Cheerleaders, Power Dancers and athlete.
workExp:
I attend major events on campus such as the Homecoming Parade, Casino Night, Freshman Convocation, Orientations, Alumni Breakfasts and more. I also enjoy giving back to the community by participating in community service programs. I love to get invitations so don’t hesitate to request an appearance at your next event. 
 
 I have also won multiple awards, such as 'Named 2022 All-American Mascot', 'Named 2019 Most Collegiate Mascot' and '2022 Top 4 NCA Collegiate Mascot in the Nation'
